s de Clientes\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2757b40 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"2757b40\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-347ad1e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"347ad1e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Cooperamos com marcas renomadas nacionais e internacionais, o que garante o alto e est\u00e1vel desempenho dos nossos equipamentos. Aceitamos a personaliza\u00e7\u00e3o de componentes-chave, incluindo motores, cilindros pneum\u00e1ticos, CLPs, engrenagens e HMIs. Venha ver o que os nossos clientes dizem sobre n\u00f3s.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f191a7 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"2f191a7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0ed21a2 elementor-testimonial--skin-default elementor-testimonial--layout-image_inline elementor-testimonial--align-center elementor-pagination-type-bullets elementor-widget elementor-widget-testimonial-carousel\" data-id=\"0ed21a2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;slides_per_view&quot;:&quot;3&quot;,&quot;slides_per_view_tablet&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;space_between&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:30,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;space_between_tablet&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:20,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;speed&quot;:10000,&quot;autoplay_speed&quot;:2000,&quot;pagination&quot;:&quot;bullets&quot;